        <item>
            <title>Bose Ultra Open Earbuds   开放式无线耳机上市</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/bose-ultra-open-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bose-ultra-open-earbuds-launched</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/bose-ultra-open-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 04:00:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Bose Ultra Open Earbuds]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220490</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在去年 1 月举行的 CES 2023，音响品牌 Bose 推出了 Ultra Open Earbuds，这款开放式无线耳机最初只作为特别版，透过美国时尚生活品牌 Kith 发售。如今 Bose 终于将 Ultra Open Earbuds 的普通版本率先于美国推出，并以 299 美元（约 2,339 港元）定价在 Amazon 等零售商上架。</p><p><span id="more-1220490"></span></p><p>作为一款开放式无线耳机，Bose Ultra Open Earbuds 的最大卖点是让用户在享受音乐的同时亦能注意周围环境。耳机采用袖珍设计，适合全天候舒适佩戴，并且兼顾到时尚的需要，可搭配帽子、眼镜或珠宝等配饰。不过 Ultra Open Earbuds 的防水等级仅 IPX4，意味著其防水等级比较适合日常佩戴，多于运动锻炼时使用。</p><p>Bose 为 Ultra Open Earbuds 配备了与 QuietComfort Ultra Earbuds 相同的驱动器，支持 Bose Immersive Audio，不过在启动后会令电池续航时间，由原本的 7.5 小时缩短至 4.5 小时。虽然支援蓝牙 5.3 和 Qualcomm aptX Adaptive 连接，但在发布时并未支援蓝牙多点连接，用户无法同时连接多部装置。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_14210"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/m6M-6u9C56c?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.bose.com/p/earbuds/bose-ultra-open-earbuds/ULT-HEADPHONEOPN.html">Bose</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/18/bose-ultra-open-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/">Bose Ultra Open Earbuds   开放式无线耳机上市</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
